                            <comment id="227386" author="gerrit" created="Sun, 6 May 2018 03:43:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Oleg Drokin (oleg.drokin@intel.com) merged in patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/32179/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/32179/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Subject: &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10575&quot; title=&quot;No mdsrate on Ubuntu client&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-10575&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-10575&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; build: make lustre-test dpkg depend on mpi-default-dev&lt;br/&gt;
